2017-04-15  <jostb@@intern>

    * build.xml, server/php/java/bridge/Util.java : Removed proxy
    
    * server/php/java/bridge/generated/JavaProxy.java: Removed
    
    * unsupported/eclipse.birt.lib: Updated to latest version
    
    * server/php/java/servlet/fastcgi/FastCGIServlet.java, server/php/java/fastcgi/FCGIProxy.java:  Send an FCGIUtil.FCGI_EMPTY_RECORD, required
      by FastCGI spec. The previous refactoring in Version 7.1.1 destroyed PHP POST requests.
    
    * VERSION, php-java-bridge.spec: Version 7.1.2 released.
    
