2008-11-13  Jost Boekemeier  <jostb@@intern>

	* server/META-INF/java/Protocol.inc
	(redirect): Send the response immediately during a context switch,
	otherwise the ContextRunner may time out after 30
	seconds. Example: java(...); wait(more than 30 seconds);
	java(...).

	* server/php/java/bridge/http/SimpleContextFactory.java
	(waitFor): Wait for the ContextRunner to finish. Otherwise the
	session may time out while the ContextRunner is running. Example
	java(...); wait(more than 30 seconds); java(...);
	$session=java_session();...

	
